<summary>🤖 Prompt for AI Agents</summary>

```
In src/lib/components/PDFViewer.svelte around lines 1013-1035 and the similar
block at 1265-1318, the stamp rendering logic is duplicated; extract a shared
async helper (e.g., renderStampsToCanvas) that accepts the
CanvasRenderingContext2D, an array of stamp annotations, canvas width/height,
and optional scale, moves the common code (legacy vs new stamp handling, SVG
retrieval, image creation, positioning, rotation, opacity, and returning null
for missing stamps) into that helper, ensures ctx.save()/ctx.restore() and
ctx.scale(scale) are applied inside the helper, returns after awaiting
Promise.all of stamp promises, and replace both original blocks with calls to
this helper (await it) preserving behavior and logs.
```

</details>

